      <h1>implicit-timezone</h1>
      <p>Returns the implicit timezone.</p>
      <p class="subhead">implicit-timezone() &#8594; xs:dayTimeDuration</p>
      <table>
         <tr>
            <td width="470" align="left" colspan="4" style="border-top:solid 1px #3D5B96; ">
